<keyLead id="30F37871FFE6562BFF60D2C8F940045B" pageId="4" pageNumber="28">—— Postfrons largely black; fore femur yellow on at least basal third; wing markings otherwise; vein 2 usually with more definite and uneven curvature ............................................................................................................... 13</keyLead>
