</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A245BA2DFFE6562BFB43D4DDF9400395" box="[1272,1323,1229,1252]" pageId="4" pageNumber="28" rank="species">n.sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BBDDB44FFE6562BFF60D4E3F94002EC" blockId="4.[219,1323,1266,1437]" pageId="4" pageNumber="28">
<keyLead id="30F37871FFE6562BFF60D4E3F94002EC" pageId="4" pageNumber="28">—— Fore femur entirely yellow; first basal cell with substantial dark mark only at distal extremity; second section of vein 4 slightly curved; penultimate section of vein 4 much shorter than anterior crossvein; distomedial lobe of mid coxa narrowed, setulose, and with one isolated strongly spinescent apical bristle; male: hind basitarsus slender, cylindrical ................................................................................ 15</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep id="30F6C3E1FFE6562BFF60D5ADF94000E4" pageId="4" pageNumber="28">
<paragraph id="8BBDDB44FFE6562BFF60D5ADF94001D3" blockId="4.[219,1323,1469,1941]" pageId="4" pageNumber="28">
<keyLead id="30F37871FFE6562BFF60D5ADF94001D3" pageId="4" pageNumber="28">
