<figureCitation id="1339C7C1FFE6562BFD97D5CAFE150283" box="[556,638,1498,1522]" captionStart="Figures 42–44" captionStartId="25.[266,338,1563,1585]" captionTargetBox="[249,1383,151,1545]" captionTargetId="figure-10@25.[249,1383,151,1545]" captionTargetPageId="25" captionText="Figures 42–44. Bama monstrans n.sp. (42) Holotype male. (43) Right wing of female. (44) Right hind leg of male." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4684913" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4684913/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="28">Fig. 43</figureCitation>
); second basal cell with apical bare spot delimited by narrow microtrichose strip; penultimate section of vein 4 more than half as long as anterior crossvein; mid coxa with elongate finger-like distomedial extension lacking marginal ridge (
<figureCitation id="1339C7C1FFE6562BFD81D65FFEE00119" box="[570,651,1615,1640]" captionStart="Figures 45–47" captionStartId="26.[627,699,1632,1654]" captionTargetBox="[121,1422,178,1743]" captionTargetId="figure-80@26.[121,1421,151,1743]" captionTargetPageId="26" captionText="Figures 45–47.Bama monstrans n.sp.(45) Distal part of aedeagus of holotype, right lateral view,scale = 0.3 mm.(46) Preglans from left side, scale = 0.1 mm.(47) Pair of mid coxae of male, left lateroventral view. bu, bulb; fs, flexible section of aedeagus; g, glans; lg, distal lobe of glans; pg, lobe of preglans; st, stipe; tf, terminal filaments." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4684915" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4684915/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="28">Fig. 47</figureCitation>
); male: wing with apical dark zone almost as extensive as in female (
<figureCitation id="1339C7C1FFE6562BFD72D67DFF7C01F4" box="[713,791,1645,1669]" captionStart="Figures 42–44" captionStartId="25.[266,338,1563,1585]" captionTargetBox="[249,1383,151,1545]" captionTargetId="figure-10@25.[249,1383,151,1545]" captionTargetPageId="25" captionText="Figures 42–44. Bama monstrans n.sp. (42) Holotype male. (43) Right wing of female. (44) Right hind leg of male." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4684913" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4684913/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="28">Fig. 42</figureCitation>
